## Optional: 1Password secret references (resolved at runtime by `op run`)
## These are NOT secrets — they are pointers. The default path is plain env vars.
## See .env.example for the standard setup.
##
## Usage: op run --env-file .env.op -- <your-command>

## Kilo Gateway auth is now handled via OAuth device login (`kilo auth login`).
## Credentials are stored in ~/.local/share/kilo/auth.json — no env var needed.
